text:
Kim Kardashian likes to play with lots of looks, and this time she chose to change her hair. She posted the new look on her Instagram Stories during last weekend.

This came right after she tweeted the following words: ‘I can’t even tell you how over my blonde hair I am!’

Kim is a natural brunette and she has been sporting a platinum blond hair for quite a while.

In a filtered video on social media, Kim asked her fans whether they love her new pink hair or not.

After that, she made sure to answer fans who were probably thinking that this is a just a wig: ‘I don’t really do wigs. It’s real.’

This major change comes after a new report has surfaced online claiming that Kim and many of her sisters are arguing because she is treating little Chi a bit different to her other two kids, North and Saint.

It’s already a known fact that Kim suffered from infertility issues and therefore turned to a surrogate to carry her third child.

According to Radar Online, Kanye West and the rest of the family members are not thrilled with Kim’s behavior.

An insider said that ‘Kanye and Kim’s sisters think she is acting completely different with baby Chicago than she did with her past kids. It is creating a lot of arguments for Kanye.’

Kanye and Kim are also fighting over the fact that Kim is reportedly already looking forward to a fourth baby via surrogate again.
